name: Captain Jonus
Lore: 'Often flies as top cover during bombing runs. Served with Death Squadron. Narrowly escaped death by space slug. Scored several kills against rebel blockade runners.',
Text: 'Deploys -2 aboard Scimitar 2. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When forfeited from a TIE/sa, also satisfies all remaining attrition and battle damage against you.',
